title: Home Values and House Prices, Westchester County New York by Municipality, January 2009
name: Home Values and House Prices, Westchester County New York by Municipality, January 2009
description: This dataset was created from the Zillow.com website of Home Values and House Prices for the municipalities of Westchester co. Various measurements are provided including the Zillow Home Value Index, the percent and $ amount change from 1 year ago and the property taxes. Values of -1 represent no data available.
